alue="give merely-possible future people no weight" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#8a5fb0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_2_5_6_7_8_14_16" target="w1_2_5_6_7_8_14_16_17"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="1509" y="2343"/><mxPoint x="1509" y="2389"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e13" value="give merely-possible future people no weight" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#8a5fb0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_2_5_6_7_8_15_16" target="w1_2_5_6_7_8_15_16_17"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="1099" y="2343"/><mxPoint x="1094" y="2389"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><object label="Suffering-focused&lt;br&gt;ethics&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+8]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   86k lives-eq/$1k · 7% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 64%&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1z27gR%2Fis7nl4rpTJFUu9y3Rknlu8ydXIZ2%2BnNTZRRIBKScCYJFgBNqznfb%2B8CICXKUmrm9EVDkcCzz75iF19PQrogWaTe8JCejE%2FabTg%2FP4c7QVgCikMgyH%2FX%2BJAnMM181%2BtCzkUUPjCaQ%2B7N%2FFlv1p8