9OTlrHMGA53fK%2Bwn38FBwYpZLJVYGyoNg5CNAsMs%2BIAUBOeWrssf8Tu2I4L0XrLb6dZ%2By5a1Z1%2Fjs0vFANJ39jgrGxmucbFu6vmlttuf2Yl7A2Ah6jtbNzhtrd9n9nF23fQhjcFpUmiBE0FjlCZQJXSCrudjuy7TLez9fttp%2Beon%2FTVEYVrSpYZ3ZLa7b1e6VLf8euabWdzs7K7ruluVzhypoB%2BxVGXwgfBf8NwqyTDTs%2Bl8d1ObafubG5Wdtdl9wt2KDiUSaQkobGyBkzx%2BMTiE1JZCbwDHZcRV5vrPkBzi1Dbmpse50pQClfm5qBizAPdlZbRq23QfYDmBqEuyZttP3MnMllx9sEmCuEPUTm01nDZk%2FcmMtcLTMAdkfdwxXH%2B38p81v18Q9ruqsNyLq6vryaXlWx%2F3q8UCb97IVS%2FAjyDa34Lr35V%2BH%2FXnxWv7LUqxymyh%2FcnNfmsm47yzD2HayTrCH15ImnD%2FNHn8Ot1w57BLfj6%2B%2BPv8OhUCD01m9NkrgPxvDy8P7mfi17m7uA9891Pb2%2B3ncrYHv66xZmXl83YAjFkoa89K1fXKEGvqEqfJidP%2FwMk6oz9" id="w1_2_5_6_7_8"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#e9b0a0;strokeColor=#b8402a;fontColor=#511810;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1073" y="70" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Resilience erodes&lt;br&gt;nuclear deterrence&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+8+11]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   86k lives-eq/$1k · 9% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 63%&lt;br&gt;▼ 11 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + resilience_undermines_deterrence&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Peltzman effect for civil defence: making nuclear war survivable weakens deterrence and raises the chance of war, so a resilient-food dollar partly insures against a catastrophe it also makes marginally likelier. An alternative, lower estimate for ALLFED, anchored to Rodriguez&#x27;s ~0.4%/yr US-Russia war probability. Requires future people to be in the circle. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_5_6_7_8_11.drawio" id="w1_2_5_6_7_8_11"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1501" y="415" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Collapse reroll:&lt;br&gt;survivors rebuild wiser&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+8+12]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   86k lives-eq/$1k · 9% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 64%&lt;br&gt;▼ 11 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + collapse_teaches_better_future&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Collapse-as-reroll, optimistic: survivors of a near-collapse rebuild wiser and more cautious, so much of the value of preventing a survivable collapse is recovered by the better rebuild — resilient-food work aimed at averting collapse is worth less. The opposite of collapse_degrades_future, so the two cannot be held together. Requires the undiscounted far future. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 12 collapse_teaches_better_future" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_5_6_7_8_12.drawio" id="w1_2_5_6_7_8_12"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1428" y="764" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Collapse reroll:&lt;br&gt;survivors stagnate&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+8+13]&lt;br&gt;→ ALLFED&lt;br&gt;   771k lives-eq/$1k · 21% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 54%&lt;br&gt;▼ 11 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + collapse_degrades_future&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Collapse-as-reroll, pessimistic: survivors become durably tech-averse and stagnate, locking in a permanently degraded future close in badness to extinction — so preventing a survivable collapse is worth much more, and resilient foods (ALLFED) can overtake AI safety. The opposite of collapse_teaches_better_future. Requires the undiscounted far future. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_5_6_7_8_13.drawio" id="w1_2_5_6_7_8_13"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1428" y="1113" width="323" height="140" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Time of perils:&lt;br&gt;space settlement exits it&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+8+14]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   930k lives-eq/$1k · 18% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 50%&lt;br&gt;(Toby Ord, Elon Musk)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + time_of_perils_exit&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Time-of-perils optimism: hazard is high during the AI / nuclear transition but collapses once decorrelated, self-sufficient settlements exist — no single catastrophe reaches them all. The window closes, the expected future stretches far past the background-hazard baseline, and x-risk reduction during the window is what unlocks it (Ord, The Precipice; the multiplanetary-backup argument). Mutually exclusive with the view that early expansion re-arms the hazard. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 14 time_of_perils_exit" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WWtz27gV%2FSt3PN1WSmWZpN523RlvLO9m6jzGcbqzE2cUiIQk1BTBAqRlbTb723sAkBIVKxOmmv3ioUjg3HOfuBf%2BdBTxGcvj7LmM%2BNHp0ckJnZ%2Bf061iIqFMUqjYb2s8rBK6ywPP79JKqjh6EHxFK38STHqT%2FmQwGU7wpaEzmZLfbRqIuwRQF1rnyzQTMqFwAcRT8ihlSoYLwWID6I8C8mnG1ISt2HqyyJcs0eWHgFgilizWEy2XfLVgWfmlR7M8yxUvNkyWLMu4mqxEtphEQocyTzKRzMvlfUpk9f1kZ3e5arARV8CxSSw3Ioek89mMK7tdhrnm0UaBLmViySdyNkmxAAD8UWTWAGMWLohtrSA0MXqzzhZ4nomYE6y8%2FaxPKDNasijSLVIcrhEJ1ySVBVP8GMZjSw5yQuN9tuDOrn%2FTMEgSWowzCuUyldrov1mAvUnEgYhXQls0nbEkYrFMOC3h%2B7hNHzeuHT98NFTNdv6Y8jDDxgcW55zkzCJso6BtwX7kOqNpvqbciDEbNa8qdkoXL0izGc%2FW1Ljh0UrKiG6wiKlw0XQYP41fjW8ubseXNF3TnCdcsYy303UZeDwS2Y6xnuFjC67NHCVjTyBZrHdJyFVmFF9KhVDb2E27tc4oLE1jwXWb3q6X7VjOE6ng%2F8antNeidNT73LRY1mcj7wd6%2FuLMrpzyjLm3qZJTNhWxyEBkKo3ykcma916L%2FA9tumJhJiGTKe6gsCA1nkiyFmlJ3ISHVHP4b%2Fx%2BdXlx%2FevJXz7QlMdyhaQwe62f%2BSOe4zW2Axu2tViQHeVh5jwCH3KEMtSfxTLHrgXcf1lEPJ0%2FVRCZ2PaGVk3zOPzcJLIhBkzosOJivgA28lZxZnNpAWuZaNTUuJVLpsX9Gf0bCplvgRd4MNYmQ94oAerw9V7JftsvBPfbvUIwf8wUq4hlD%2FCfgYbOPEEwbbC%2FLt5ldUVr30KneHlsEpT%2BTiHLmM6UTGExk%2BRJzmxemnRk6tghFKHeuGFLzdcnbxE2Cf3h%2FXCyVvSg6ZVU0YLlmv7w2z3z8gyCzhGHVJYYcHGFYIw68BLFVZg4U%2FutERS26HiFKXTIYn6cp6VnNxlYsBPu9YL9xhQ8BRsgWsJYmkhhM5ClpRPJEgSqWpPmWRbzJYKOGq9VhGCz1g