etry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Living in&lt;br&gt;a simulation&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7+8+14+16]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   93k lives-eq/$1k · 6% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up Shrimp Welfare Project · 63%&lt;br&gt;(Nick Bostrom)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + time_of_perils_exit + living_in_simulation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 14 time_of_perils_exit → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy9WWtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6u3XUcyW8nmwXSxpkpNn0gTXcwaAqXlmibG0nUklIcT6fz2%2FeQlGy5dlHNBpgvgUKR55775L3y56OQz1keZS9kyI9Oj05O6Pz8nG4VEwllkgLFfl3jYZXQXd7x%2FB6tpIrCB8FXtPKnnWl%2FOpgOp6Op35v6A2roTKbkD5oG5S4B2oXWeZxmQiYULAF6Sh6lTMlgKVhkMP1xh3yaMzVlK7aeLvOYJbp80SGWiJhFeqplzFdLlpVv%2BjTPs1zx4sA0ZlnG1XQlsuU0FDqQeZKJZFFuH1Aiq%2BvTndPlruFGXAHHppHciByRzudzruxxGeSahxsFepSJmE%2FlfJpiAwD4o9gchGEi8WCOiWSqRZxHzBjE2mfCgiWxrZGEJkZv19kSz3MRcYIftq%2F1CWXGCCwMdYsUh%2FNEwjVJZcEUP4ZtWczBXWisZ0vuzP43DXslgcU4o0DGqdTGPJsNOJuEHIhYEtqi6YwlIYtkwilGdERt%2BrRx%2FuThk6FqjvPHlAcZDj6wKOck5xZhGydtC%2Fac64xm%2BZpyI8Yc1Lyq2CldvCTN5jxbU%2BOGhyspQ7rBJqaCZdNh%2FDh5Pbm5uJ1c0mxNC55wxTLeTtdlaPIQNq8a6xletuD5zFEy9gSSxXqfBFxlRvFYKkTixm7a7XVGYWkaCa7b9G4dtyO5SKRCeDQ%2Bp%2F0WpeP%2Bl6bFsj4bez%2FQi5dndueMZ8ytpkrO2ExEIgORmTTKhyavPngt8j%2B26YoFmYRMpriDwobUeCLJWqQlcRMeUi3gv8mH1eXF9S8nf