ation ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 14 time_of_perils_exit → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy9WWtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6u3XEcyW8nmwXSxpkpNm2DNN1i0BQuLdE2J5KoJaU4nk762%2FeQkmy5UVF1DcyXQKHIc8998l7584HP5ywNkhfS5wfHB0dHdHp6SjeKiYgSSZ5if6zxsIroNu04bo9WUgX%2BveArWrnTzrQ%2FHUyH09HU7U3dITV0ImNyh02DchsB7UzrNIwTISPylgA9JodipqS3FCwwmO64Qy7NmZqyFVtPl2nIIl286BCLRMgCPdUy5KslS4o3fZqnSap4fmAasiTharoSyXLqC%2B3JNEpEtCi2DyiS5fXpzuli13AjLodj00BuRI5Ip%2FM5V%2Fa49FLN%2FY0CPUpEyKdyPo2xAQD8QWwOwjBY1TKaMpz3rHxjQWugCfOWxLZWEpoYXa2TJZ7nIuAER2xf6yNKjBWY7%2BsWKQ7viYhrksqCKX4I47KQg7zQWE%2BWPLP7PzQMFnkW44Q8GcZSG%2FtsNuBs5HMgYkloi6YTFvkskBGnEOERtOnTxvuT%2B0%2BGqjnOH2IohYP3LEg5yblF2AZK24I95zqhWbqm1IgxBzUvK3ZMb5dKhDG95wGigdOVkr8DNzv9y%2BT15PrsZnJOszUteMQVS3g7XhdRyX2Yu2ymZ3jZgtOTjIyxJJAs1rvI4yoxKodSIQg3FtPZ3swcLI4DwXWb3q7DdiAXkVSIjMbnuN%2BieNx%2FbFos662x8xO9eHlid854wrLVWMkZm4lAJCAyk0Zt36TUB6dF7sc2XTAvkZAJXTMobIiND6KkRVoSN4Eh1QKem3xYnZ9d%2Fnb0t48044FcIV3MWeth%2FoDnYI3jwIZVLRZk%2B6mXZL6A9ziCHOrPA5ni1BKOP89zgU6fKogcbTsjq6Z5HD02iWxwARM6rLhYLIGNjFac2SxbwlomDjU1bmTItLg7of9AIfOu43QcGGuTO1dKgHqyrpbstt1c8KDdzwXzh0Sxklh2D%2F8ZaOjMI4TRBvvb4rN8L2ntWugYi4cmdeln8ljCdKJkDIuZ9I9SZjPSJCJThxlCHuSNaxZqvj56i7CJ6Ivz09Fa0b2m11L5S5Zq%2BuK2%2B2bxBIJOEYdUFB9wyUrEBBXiFSqvMHGmqq3RyW3RdXJTaI8F%2FDCNC89uci9nJ7LlJfuDKXgKNkC0eI