lation ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzNWWtz2zYW%2FSt3PNuulFoyKVkve70zTiy3mXVSj%2BNsphNnFIiEJNQUwQVIy2qa%2FPYegA9RET1hVl%2F6xUOTwLnnPnEv9OnA5zOWBPEL6fODk4OjIzo7O6NbxURIsSRPsT%2FWeFiFdJd0HPeYVlIF%2FoPgK1q5k86kN%2BlPBpPhxO1N3P7EHVBDxzIid9A0QHchAM%2B1TpZRLGRI3gK4J%2BRQxJT0FoIFBtYddcilGVMTtmLrySJZslDnHzrEQrFkgZ5oueSrBYvzLz2aJXGieLZhsmRxzNVkJeLFxBfak0kYi3CeL%2B9TKMvvJ1u781WDQlwGxyaBLEQOSSezGVd2u%2FQSzf1CgR7piHl8wh8j4EHbyZR59zOheAHu9ikQD2azCCdaLJOAWbPknwcUcaWxk0GIZ0kaS1srjpm3ILYxpdDE6HodL%2FA8EwEnOGzzWR9RbEzFfF8fkuLwsghBRCoLpngLHmBLDg2Fxvt4wVPn%2FFPDqqFnMU7Jk8tIamPEYgH2hj4HIl4JbdF0zEKfBTLktEQYBW36WETJ%2BOGjoWq2wzBQChsfWJBwkjOLsAmotgV7znVM02RNiRFjNmpeVuyE3iyUWEb0jgcIGU7XSv4O3HT3z%2BPX45vz2%2FEFTdc05yFXLObtaJ1HL%2FdFvGWmZ%2Fh4iMiIUzLGkkCyWG9Dj6vYqLyUCpFaWEyna1NzsCgKBNdterNetgM5D6VC%2BDQ%2BRb1Dika9z02LZb01cn6gFy9P7copj1n6NlJyyqYiEDGITKVR2zep9945JPdDmy6ZF0vIhK4pFBZExgdhfEhaEjeBIdUcnhu%2FX12cX%2F129I8PNOWBXCGnzF7rYf6I52CN7cCGVS0WZPuJF6e%2BgPc4IhfqzwKZYNcCjr%2FIEobOdhVEIredoVXTPA4%2FN4lscAETOqy4mC%2BAjbRXnNlUXMBaJg41NW7lkmlxf0r%2FhULmW8fpODBWkWDXSoB6vK6W7LbdTHC%2F3csE88dYsZJY9gD%2FGWjozEOEUYH9tPi0KJS0di10hJetWCw5%2FUQei5mOlYxgMVMjwiTNYpOITLVShCzIGzdsqfn66A3CJqQvzg9Ha0UPml5L5S9Youm