mulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbO7jmKJL8nlwPSxNktLu0GSXrFoilcWqItbiRRR1JRvN3sb98hKdly7KLqGfvFkCXymWdeOcMvByGdkzxW5zykB8cHR0dwenoKd4KwFBSHQJDflvhQpHCf%2B67Xg4KLOHxktIDCm%2FrT%2FnQwHU5HU28ALal4Bt6grSHuU4Q6kzJPMsV4CkGEiMfgQkYEDyJGYg3ojX3wYE7ElBRkOY3yhKSy%2BuADSVlCYjmVPKFFRFT1pQ%2FzXOWClhumCVGKimnBVDQNmQx4niqWLqrlA0h5%2Ff10Y3e1argSV8KRacxXIkcg8%2FmcCrOdB7mk4UqBAcTsUX9g6VSyJI%2BJVtlYYEKCCMjaDEwCgeulivB5zmIKaOb1Z3kESqtJwlB2QFD0DUupBC4MmKCHaD2SUGTHJL5XEbWG%2FYdEi6SBwTiBgCcZl9oAqwW4Nw0pIuIrJg2aVCQNScxTCgk6P3bg88q3k8fPmqreTp8yGijc%2BEjinAKfG4R1GDgG7DWVCmb5EnItRm%2BUtK7YMdxGgiUZfKAxupvCteC%2FIq7d%2FePk3eTm7G5yAbMlLGhKBVHUyZZVzNGQqQ0zvcKPHfSqsmS0JRHJYL1PAyqUVjnhAqNsZTFp11pzkCyLGZUO3C4TJ%2BaLlAt0fetL1u9ANu4%2Ftw2W8dbY%2FQHO35yYlTOqiH2bCT4jMxYzhURmXKsd6oT56HbA%2B%2BTAJQkUR5moq4XCBZn2Qao6IDlQHRhcLNBzk4%2FFxdnVL0d%2F%2BwQzGvMC80HvNR6mT%2FgcL3E7YqNVDRbKDvNAWV%2Bg9yhGMao%2Fj3mOuyJ0%2FEUZ7HC6rSAmoeOOjJr6cfTcBjDBhZioQ0HZIkJsTFlBiUmjCK2l41BC644nRLKHE%2FgvKqS%2F%2Ba7vorFWyXEtGFJXy92SPccrBQ%2BcfimYPilBamLJI%2FpPQ6PONMUwWmF%2FXbxN6JrWnoHO8OWhYgmFf0JAFJFK8AwtpvM7zU2WaokYkIcWoQzy1g1JJF0e3WLYpPCH%2B8PRUsCjhHdchBHJJfzhOX398gQFnWIcQlVdtClWFeCc63KToxtPV9HTQgOMreLXrfVSEDlWIkzGBdCU54sI5tykkSZXVrt2lQ6vuVYkQeXdbhn1F0xgNgFFSwXGirX4yjDxiFhicKVYTwKGzx14Pbn8%2BWZic8QgWAegTTuYaRjgCdbcVB1iLQwiDIuVI%2BH2%2Fdu3Zze%2F2OjDYmWFYD14oKFBmnFFA2jpsISzdxdoU8EIZqUN5rYDd1qtPI7LQD%2BcLQ%2FtE2DtYI%2FWIFZXSw3rulXILjM68UeaGlSsYphQucDH0j5YjdHm%2BgBDQTFLK2LyfzlbLGJ6ZBjKo3%2Bx8N9O9dIWQZObWGwwx3XRQcUR5ud3E8hiYmWVlZiEulZRjNXluhZizSYoUzsOdWcpyjYImLt2pS20GCM8z%2F7DtGXTCxIvr6l4L8PdKTNwBv543B31xyPP7w5djx66%2FVX2uq43HI%2BG3Z7nDod9zx96vTKtXvgPa6cJgrJmaALTB8tgw2F%2Ff%2BmuE%2BuqtWeOt%2BxYB1vZ8z5dhN%2FSTfN3ezVl