t;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy9WWtv2zgW%2FSsXwc6u3XEcyY5f6WaBNHFmik07QZJuMWgKl5ZomxtJ1JJSHG8n%2Fe17SEm2XKuougbmS6CI5LnnPnmv%2FPnA5zOWBsm59PnBycHREZ2entKdYiKiRJKn2H9XeFhGdJ92HPeYllIF%2FqPgS1q6k86kN%2BlPBpPhxO1P3AE1dCJjcgdNg3IfAe1M6zSMEyEj8hYAPSGHYqaktxAsMJjuqEMuzZiasCVbTRZpyCJdLHSIRSJkgZ5oGfLlgiXFSo9maZIqnh%2BYhCxJuJosRbKY%2BEJ7Mo0SEc2L7X2KZPn9ZOt0sWuwFpfDsUkg1yKHpNPZjCt7XHqp5v5agT4F4tEsiGiiRZgGzKpcLA8o5krLaMIA4FkCxoTWQmPmLYhtzCQ0MbpeJQs8z0TACZ7YLOsjSowZmO%2FrFikO94mIa5LKgil%2BCOuykIO90HifLHhm%2BL9pWCzyLMZL8mQYS20MtN6As5HPgYhXQls0nbDIZ4GMOIWIj6BNn9buHz9%2BMlTNcf4UQykcfGRByknOLMImUtoW7BXXCU3TFaVGjDmoeVmxE7pdKBHG9J4HCAdO10r%2BG7jZ6V%2FGb8c3Z3fjC5quaM4jrljC2%2FGqCEvui2TLTC%2Bw2ILXk4yMsSSQLNa7yOMqMSqHUiEK1xbT2d7MHCyOA8F1m25XYTuQ80gqhEbjc9xrUTzqPTctlvXWyPmJzl%2B%2FtDunPGHZ21jJKZuKQCQgMpVGbd%2Fk1AenRe7HNl0yL5GQCV0zKGyIjQ%2BipEVaEjeBIdUcnht%2FWF6cXf1%2B9JePNOWBXCJfzFnrYf6E52CF48CGVS0WZPupl2S%2BgPc4ohzqzwKZ4tQCjr%2FIk4FOdxVEkradoVXTPA6fm0Q2uIAJHZZczBfARkorzmyaLWAtE4eaGncyZFo8vKR%2FQSGz1nE6Doy1Tp5rJUA9WVVLdttuLrjf7uWC%2BVOiWEkse4T%2FDDR05hHCaI39bfFZwpe0di10jJeHiQg5%2FUweS5hOlIxhMZP%2FUZplsUlEpg4zhDzIGzcs1Hx1dIuwieiL89PRStGjprdS%2BQuWavritnvm5UsIOkUcUlF9jCnWFeJcmnKUwo2n6%2